This folder contains screenshots demonstrating vulnerability findings before remediation and validation results after applying STIG remediation scripts.

Each subfolder represents a phase of the remediation process:
- Initial scan
- Identified findings
- Remediation execution
- Validation scan
- Post-remediation results

Note:
The WinVerifyTrust finding required remediation across both 64-bit and 32-bit registry paths.
Initial remediation did not resolve the issue until both paths were configured and the system was rebooted.
